<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16270</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美罗城的某一个早晨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16271</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一辆车开进工地，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23559</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>三名建筑工人从车里走下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23560</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28262</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们正在建一座新的高楼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28263</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们今天有很多活儿要干。”一个男人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33515</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39160</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，工人们听到什么声音。嗡！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39161</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是什么声音？”一个女人问。嗡！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们看！”另一位男人大叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“新大楼正在变小！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西和朋友们走在上学的路上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们路过了落基山面包店。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68828</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯......”玛拉说，“面包闻起来真香！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们放学后买些饼干吧。”特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好主意。”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看！”玛拉说，“那里就是美罗城电影院。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84583</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉指向一栋旧大楼，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大楼的窗户都被木板盖住了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>墙壁上都是裂纹，楼前长满了杂草。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我听说旧电影院关门了。”杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102739</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在这里看过很多电影。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102740</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也是。”特勒尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过现在，市内有了一个新电影院。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>里面有十二个厅！还有3D电影！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也在旧电影院看过很多电影。”玛拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123872</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是现在，我父母希望拆了它。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123873</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127315</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么？”杰克问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127316</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132808</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为大家想在那里建一个社区花园。”玛拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132809</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136296</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们想种水果和蔬菜。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136297</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139774</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那一定很漂亮。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139775</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“花园一定比旧楼好看。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149197</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉点头。“不过，工人得先把它拆了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149198</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔眼睛一亮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们应该叫火箭女孩儿来帮忙！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她能拆掉那个旧电影院！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159572</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西转了转眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿肯定有更重要的事情去做。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔皱了皱眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许，你是对的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过，我相信她能做到。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182804</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，罗西的手表响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182805</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184625</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看着朋友们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184626</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”罗西说，“我带午饭钱了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西停下脚步，假装翻背包。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196545</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，按下手表上的按钮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196546</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199398</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布洛姆市长。”她小声问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199399</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有什么事吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿！”市长说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“美罗城的新摩天大楼不见了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207977</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不见了？”罗西不解地问，“怎么回事？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它变小后不见了。”市长说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“工人看到......不好了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布洛姆市长！”罗西说，“发生什么事了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“救救我们，火箭女孩儿！”布洛姆市长声音突然低下来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“救救我们！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241173</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布洛姆市长？布洛姆市长？”罗西叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241174</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>市长没有回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么了？”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>